Constant Story "Desperados";
Constant Headline "^Kenneth Johnson trilogy #3^Copyright (c) 2025 Gianluca Girelli and Garry Francis^Type ABOUT for further info and credits.^^";

Array UUID_ARRAY string "UUID://9ead9613-bc13-4c62-af3d-186247a78d9e//";
